DOC.brief_summary: The objective of this study is to evaluate the effect of multiple doses of BI 207127 combined with faldaprevir on cardiac safety parameters in healthy subjects
DOC.brief_title: Thorough QT Study to Evaluate the Effects of BI 207127 (Deleobuvir) Combined With Faldaprevir on Cardiac Safety Parameters in Healthy Subjects.
DOC.criteria: Inclusion criteria: Healthy male and female subjects Subjects must be able to understand and comply with study requirements Age =18 and =55 years BMI range: =18.5 and =29.9 kg/m2 Exclusion criteria: any relevant deviation from healthy conditions
